The website should be able to filter the price range, brand, and similar criteria chosen by the users.

The website should be able to compare up to 4 items and view them on a single page.

The website should display the most compared products on its front page.

All specifications need to have a short explanation of what they do. For example, an HDD/SSD stores data and a CPU does the processing.
	
The user can create their own profile within site to leave reviews and ratings and save their comparisons. Other users can look at their profiles and look at their reviews.

 Users can guide other users by sharing their ideas and experiences about products on their profiles. 

The website should be easy to navigate through with a simple interface.

